<h4>Writing a description:</h4>
<p>The description should include enough information for anyone to know what you were thinking of for this article and why it is relevant for The Teen Magazine's target demographic. Include links to any places where you got the idea from (ie. Quora, Reddit, other blog articles etc.). If it's an advice article, specify the type of writer this topic is best suited for. For example, an article about how to write your college application should be written by a writer who is, or has already gone through, the process.</p>
<p>If you did a search analysis for this article topic, include the target search term/phrase. Explain what the current search results are and what the writer who claims this topic needs to do to outperform existing articles (ie. list more examples, be more in-depth, more specific, better researched etc.).</p>
<p>Be specific and in-depth. Your description should be around 60-120 words.</p>

